Explanation of how it works the Final Project if you want to play:
1. Select the option: "Instructions"
   Read carefully how it works and what you have to do.
   Go "back" after it.
2. Afterwords, you select the option "Play". Move your nose along the court.
3. Press the key space to pick up one ball and drag it tou the goal (the same color).
4. Repeat this action as faster as you can with all the balls.
5. Have fun! 
